1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Nc3 Be7 {What is the better move for White: 4. Bc4 or 4. 
Nb5?} 4. Bc4 {This is a good move - developing a piece and preparing to castle.} 
(4. Nb5 {is a bad move and Deadly Sin number 2 - moving the same piece more than 
once. This is just a pointless move! After} 4... Nf6 {Black is already ahead in 
development.}) *

