1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 d6 3. Nc3 Nf6 4. Bc4 g6 5. d3 Bg7 6. O-O h5 {Develop White's 
last minor piece to an active square.} 7. Bg5 {[%cal Gg5d8][%csl Rf6] Good. On 
this square the Bishop pins the Knight and cannot be attacked by a Pawn.} (7. 
Be3 {This is OK but less active.}) (7. Bd2 {The Bishop is too passive here.}) *

